| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0470 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6affc09d-1f6f-5133-8ea4-124ad3ec5fdb"
